# ── PRD / internal product docs (keep out of GitHub) ─────────────────
# Matches any file with "prd" in the name, any case (e.g. PRD.md,
# nm_data_officer_dashboard_prd.md, product-PRD.md). README.md is kept.
*[Pp][Rr][Dd]*.md
*[Pp][Rr][Dd]*.docx
*[Pp][Rr][Dd]*.pdf
prd/
docs/prd/
!README.md

